<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.5">
<l>aḻakiya vāyila muta vūṟaṟ ṟeḷivuṟā</l>
<l>maḻalaimuṟ ṟāta viḷañcollā luṉṉaik kūvukiṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>kuḻakaṉ cirītaraṉ kūvak kūvanī pōtiyēl</l>
<l>puḻaiyila vākā tēniṉ cevipukar māmatī</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He calls you with immature young words,</l>
<l>prattling indistinctly with trickling nectar on his beautiful lips.</l>
<l>Big, bright Moon, if you leave as the beautiful Śrīdhara calls and calls,</l>
<l>your ears are without holes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
